ch his Honour refers are those of Kerr J in }{\b\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Surrendra Overseas Limited v Government of Sri Lanka (The Apjakash)}{\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  [1977] 2 All ER 481 where his Lordship stated:

