\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri331\sl240\slmult0\widctlpar\faauto\rin331\lin0\itap0 {\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 15\tab On 28 May 2003 the Magistrate handed down his decision.  At para 30 he stated:
