\b\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Electronic Transaction Act}{\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  also applied.  It is common ground that the }{\b\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Electronic Transaction Act}{
\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  did not have retrospective operation and came into force in December 2001.  As such, the }{\b\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Electronic Transaction Act}{\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
